        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I would like to use Zend_Locale's default locale to set up Zend_Currency in bootstrap. However Zend_Currency is somehow missing '_FI' ending from 'fi_FI' giving the fatal error: 'No region found within the locale 'fi'' in [...]\/Zend\/Currency.php:548\r\n\r\n{code:title=application.ini}\r\nresources.locale.default = \"fi_FI\"\r\n{code}\r\n\r\n{code:title=bootstrap.php}\r\nprotected function _initViewHelpers() {\r\n    ...\r\n    $this->bootstrap('locale');\r\n    $locale = $this->getResources('locale');\r\n    $currency = new Zend_Currency(null, $locale);\r\n    Zend_Registry::set('Zend_Currency', $currency);\r\n}{code}\r\n\r\nOf course I can always use Zend_Currency('fi_FI'), but..."
        },
